Package com.commander4j.messages

Class GenericMessageHeader

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.messages.GenericMessageHeader
public class GenericMessageHeader extends Object
All Commander4j xml messages have a standard format. The header section describes the content (data) component of the message.
